items.title: Body found confirmed to be missing teen, death ruled suicide
items.description: A body found in Texas on Tuesday has been identified as 19-year-old Camila Mendoza Olmos, who had been missing for nearly one week.

items.title: ACA subsidies that lower monthly premiums for millions of Americans set to expire
